{"tid":2498020,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一日前的雲加：我預料歐超聯不會走得很遠","createTime":"2021-04-21T01:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T05:12:34.000Z","uid":272077,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a82a782ed1ec83cdf406b790d25afca8fe855c79","tid":2498020,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:39:21.000Z","msg":"'This idea will not go far' - Ex-Arsenal boss Wenger casts doubt over Super League<br />\n<br />\nArsenal are among those to have signed up, as part of the Premier League's 'Big Six', with three sides from Italy and as many from Spain also getting involved in a project that Wenger - who now fills a role at FIFA - cannot see getting off the ground.<br />\n<br />\nWenger, who spent 22 years as Gunners boss and is now FIFA's head of global development, told talkSPORT: &quot;I would say that&rsquo;s a bad idea. Football has to stay united, it&rsquo;s the most important thing.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;It&rsquo;s based on sporting merit and overall to respect the history that has been built from European football.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">&quot;I believe, personally, that this idea will not go far.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&quot;I don&rsquo;t know what exactly is behind (it). There is a more dangerous idea behind it and it&rsquo;s a big threat for the Premier League.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;When I was still in charge it was a lot going on from other countries to diminish the dominance of the Premier League and a project like that would certainly accelerate that.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c548e64334a74c252c3dd2974a6f779fd451767c","tid":2498020,"uid":7179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1cadce83aee7c5c1bf2905af86b76966fba314","tid":2498020,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"同雲加一樣 最多走到亞軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4647249a9f4224cfb9d971ca1c84774d2fe531","tid":2498020,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4257ce4473c4d8a40462f2eedf5b351004fcbe21","tid":2498020,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc1cadce83aee7c5c1bf2905af86b76966fba314","tid":2498020,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"同雲加一樣 最多走到亞軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"4哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fe50627741b59cd279712a17bf3659d10dde9a","tid":2498020,"uid":313162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"yaya<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccb8769d63fcdfc5a4dd80df39dfdca5079489a","tid":2498020,"uid":364705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:55:46.000Z","msg":"經濟學大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e4239f5b25360f4ae891aaaad0351d8e13f678","tid":2498020,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:56:31.000Z","msg":"雲加！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbfcc25b1e153bb451c6dae62e8869bd0582f34","tid":2498020,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:56:56.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90c184413a972bf21af9d82fad4ce688ab15e09","tid":2498020,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s